item.title: I-10 West - Continental Divide
item.description: Continental Divide on I-10 west - Elevation 4,585 Feet. This is the dividing line between the Gila River (flows to Colorado River) and the Mimbres River (flows into a closed basin).

item.title: I-10 West - Entering Gila River Watershed
item.description: Entering Gila River Watershed on I-10 west. The Gila River flows to the Colorado River. This is the Continental Divide.

item.title: US-180 West/NM-26 East at I-10
